SPF/WBPLA World Powerlifting and Bench Press Championship 2009 Results

Results for SPF/WBPLA World Championship 10/03 - 04/09  I would like to take a moment to thank all the great lifters for coming out and taking part in this meet. I would also like to thank all of our Staff: Judges, Louie Simmons, Joe Ladnier, Sam Byrd, and Keith Taylor, all of our Loader/Spotters, Brent Pickett, Big Nick, Russ Curtis, Nathion Williams, Keith Taylor, Jason Davis, and Jamie McDougal on Sunday. A huge thank you goes to Barb Page for a great job announcing on Saturday. This was her first time and talking about a great job. Also thank you Melissa Garrett for taking over and announcing and help running the table on Sunday after lifting all day on Saturday. As always thanks to Victoria Rodgers, my wife, for running the score table and keeping all the numbers right. This is a job I wouldn't want and she has always done a great job for me and the liftrers. I hope I haven't forgotten anyone but if I have, THANK YOU, it takes everyone working together to run a great meet and you people are the best.
